[04/12/2019 16:30:14] <font color="#ffffff">Uniforme.</font>
[04/12/2019 16:30:14] <font color="#00ff00">¡Correcto, uniforme!</font>
[04/12/2019 16:30:18] <font color="#ffff00">¡Uniforme, lo ha dicho!</font>
